                  <idno facs="AQM/001/AQM-001" n="43" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/api/iiif/ESaqm001/manifest">AQM-035</idno>
               </msIdentifier>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Māmās "Vita of Māmās" (fols. 3ra-24rb)
 II) Taʾammǝra Māmās
                     "Miracles of Māmās": 13 miracles (fols. 1ra-2rb and 24rb-39va) 
 
                     Additiones 1-3.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3ra" to="39va"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6481DossierMamas">Hagiographic Dossier of Māmās</title> 
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="3ra" to="24rb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6470GadlaMamas">Gadla Māmās za-Gʷǝdgʷǝdā</title>  
                        <note>Text I ("Vita of Mamas") does not contain the last chapter (kidan-scene)
                           as presented in<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESaqm002">AQM-002</ref> (<locus from="24va" to="29ra">24va-29ra</locus>).</note>
                        
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="1ra" to="2rb"/>
                        <locus from="24rb" to="39va"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6471TaammeraMamas">Taʾammǝra Māmās</title> 
                        <note>In Text II ("Miracles of Mamas") most of the miracles are numbered. The
                           8th miracle is missing in<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESaqm002">AQM-002</ref>.
                           The 12th miracle begins on <locus target="#38vb">38vb</locus> l.5. Its
                           explicit differs from the miracle presented in<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESaqm002">AQM-002</ref>(<locus from="38ra" to="38vb">38ra-38vb</locus>). Here, ʾabuna Bǝrhān Moʿa is mentioned as
                           commissioner "of this book". Furthermore the 13th miracle ends differently
                           than in<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESaqm002">AQM-002</ref>(<locus from="42va" to="43rb">42va-43rb</locus>) and is followed by an ʾarke-hymn.</note>
                        
                     </msItem>
                     
                    
                  </msItem>
                
               </msContents>
